title: Taiwan Wholesale Prices YoY
description: Wholesale Prices YoY in Taiwan decreased to 11.09 percent in October from 12.82 percent in September of 2022. Wholesale Prices YoY in Taiwan averaged 3.28 percent from 1953 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 67.33 percent in February of 1974 and a record low of -13.99 percent in July of 2009. The wholesale price index is to measure the average changes in selling prices of materials semi finished and finished goods for Taiwan area. This page includes a chart with historical data for Taiwan Wholesale Prices YoY.
author: Taiwan
